{"tid":654102,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手]菲林過機場x光會唔會有事？","createTime":"2018-05-05T10:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T12:45:41.000Z","uid":88028,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b12ad90e1aac9d962fb195421569888977151e52","tid":654102,"uid":88028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去日本同歐洲，第一次帶菲林去影<br />\n我主要都係用fujifilm 200同400<br />\n其實就咁放落袋hand carry會唔會出事？<br />\n<br />\n上網見人話400以下係ok<br />\n本身諗住hand check，但驚去到歐洲唔比<br />\n又話搵個防xray菲林袋裝住<br />\n海關反而照唔清會加大個幅射率<br />\n<br />\n求高人指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48e981dbb100593aa79ad7b53d9351f227ff459","tid":654102,"uid":1049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"hand carry,不要放入喼<br />\n低過1600 iso 唔會有事<br />\n高iso菲林或者想最穩陣，可以拎出定出黎，要求手check<br />\n係日本買過1600 iso即棄相機，返香港個陣要求日本海關手check，無問長問短，其他菲林就照過機，有左用有未用，曬出黎無分別。<br />\n咩鉛袋個d無用過，但hand carry過機照到黑色一舊一定叫你拎出黎，仲會懷疑你身有屎，所以唔洗用。要用我諗係for放入喼先用，但唔知會唔會有問題，睇下有無其他巴打答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74c4ab6bbce68b25a1dc87e58b029dffab2015d","tid":654102,"uid":160934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"hand carry / 寄倉都試過好多次<br />\n無特別保護就咁擺入袋<br />\n暫時完全無出過事"},{"pid":"7e401c73f760003ca3c8956374389a7ce1d17b51","tid":654102,"uid":88028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a74c4ab6bbce68b25a1dc87e58b029dffab2015d","tid":654102,"uid":160934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"hand carry / 寄倉都試過好多次<br />\n無特別保護就咁擺入袋<br />\n暫時完全無出過事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"巴打菲林幾多iso?"},{"pid":"66f66bae9e89c54d4ea144bd81f9d136d50d0ebe","tid":654102,"uid":12176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母躝入菲林post問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82230245d